    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "技能",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">普通攻擊</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/21/125391187/94aa30ae75b8c7c6a9c64ab05bd5dda7_686700276492581682.png",
                "id": "talent23302",
                "key": "熠輝軌度劍",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "熠輝軌度劍"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>生成<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">安眠帷幕護盾</span>和<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">飛星</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">安眠帷幕護盾</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">出戰狀態</span></p><p>提供2點<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">護盾</span>，保護我方出戰角色。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">飛星</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出戰狀態</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">我方角色使用技能後：</span>累積1枚<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">「晚星」</span>。如果<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">「晚星」</span>已有至少4枚，則消耗4枚<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">「晚星」</span>，造成1點<span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">冰元素傷害</span>。（生成此出戰狀態的技能，也會觸發此效果）</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">重複生成此出戰狀態時：</span>累積2枚<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">「晚星」</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/21/125391187/de48c78ad3dc782b2dfe98bbe645f7cd_4076834563042223160.png",
                "id": "talent46168",
                "key": "垂裳端凝之夜",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "垂裳端凝之夜"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆發</span></p><p>造成3點<span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">冰元素傷害</span>，召喚<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">飾夢天球</span>。</p><p></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/21/125391187/1af1d6edbe77aedd11a2e57551afb598_3205856551345945463.png",
                "id": "talent86843",
                "key": "星流搖床之夢",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "星流搖床之夢"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">召喚物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結束階段：</span>造成1點<span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">冰元素傷害</span>。如果<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">飛星</span>在場，則使其累積1枚<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">「晚星」</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：2</span></p><p></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/21/125391187/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_5108728850353661529.png",
                "id": "talent64829",
                "key": "飾夢天球",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/21/125391187/ac654c8b46eb850fcb5afba4ab4f6407_2153301810871915035.gif",
                "title": "飾夢天球"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附著<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>，可發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">融化</span>：本傷害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超導</span>：本傷害+1，對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">穿透傷害</span></p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">凍結</span>：本傷害+1，使目標本回合無法行動（受到<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>傷害后提前解除，但是傷害+2）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/21/125391187/4bcc4b82a9d7ee22770f60afa54e9919_6920596107439936688.png",
                "id": "talent82256",
                "key": "冰元素傷害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "冰元素傷害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理傷害</span></strong></p><p>物理傷害不會附著元素，也不會發生元素反應。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果觸發後，會消耗一層可用次數；</p><p>可用次數耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/21/125391187/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_50482736693651949.png",
